Planned Features

- Distributed Cron Scheduler with failover
- Crontab can be edited from any node (like crontab -e)
- Crontab locking across nodes (like vipw)
- Cronjobs can be scheduled with a second resolution
- Host Specifications
- Hostgroups (like YP/NIS)
- Optional job timeouts
- Optional job locking (so no two jobs of the same instance can run at the same time)
